Introduction to  internship and the possibilities of passing it. Preparation and coordination of an internship plan. Internship in a company. Preparation and defense of an internship report.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of the internship is to get acquainted with the real work environment related to informatics and information technology applications and acquire additional professional skills.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  After completing internship the student  is able to work in an information technology (IT) oriented company. He/she has: * experineced a daily work routine in IT focused entrepreneurship avtivities and enviroment; * got to know the peculiarities of working in an IT company; * developed a sense of duty and responsibility in the performance of duties; * developed communication skills with co-workers and customers; * used the knowledge and learning ability he has acquired so far; * an understanding of connections and applicability of what has been learned so far in solving work tasks. The student has an overview of a specific (IT) job and its role in  a structure of a company and career opportunities in IT companies.
